snippet: A major Qaeda-linked terrorist probably survived an airstrike last month, despite claims by the Philippine military that he had been killed, a senior Malaysian police official said.
lead_paragraph: A major Qaeda-linked terrorist probably survived an airstrike last month, despite claims by the Philippine military that he had been killed, a senior Malaysian police official said.

headline.seo: Zulkifli Was Not Killed in Filipino Airstrike, Malaysian Official Says
headline.main: Terrorist Was Not Killed in Airstrike, Malaysian Official Says
headline.print_headline: Terrorist Was Not Killed in Airstrike, Malaysian Official Says
